title: Whalen, Augustus need to get going for Lynx in WNBA Finals
text: > Indiana Whalen, Augustus need to get going for Lynx in WNBA Finals In this Oct. 4, 2015, photo, Minnesota Lynx’s Seimone Augustus, right, drives around Indiana Fever’s Briann January in the second half in Game 1 of the WNBA basketball finals in Minneapolis. Lynx coach Cheryl Reeve says the team has to get more out of stars Lindsay Whalen and Augustus on offense as the WNBA Finals progresses. The Lynx trail the Indiana Fever 1-0 in the best-of-five series. (AP Photo/Jim Mone)
